author: @muhammadabdullahdilshad8509
text: Notes -----------------------------> nums = [1,2,3,4,5] ################ For Loops #################### for nums in nums:     if nums == 3:         print("Found !")         break # Breaks out of the Loop         #If We use continue it will skip tot he enxt iteration without going any furthur     else:         print("Not Found")     print(nums)  nums = [1,2,3,4,5]  ##Nested Loops  for myval in nums:     for letter in 'abc':         print(myval,letter)   #Range Loops for x in range (10):     print(x)  for x in range (1,10): #Explicitley tell where to start the Loop     print(x)   ###########  While Loops ##################### x = 0 while x < 10:     print(x)     x +=1      # To create an infintie loop until a conmdition is met  x = 0 while(True):     if(x == 5):         print("The Condition has met ")         break     print(x)     x +=1
